    "Scramble the radio frequency.....useing it was her downfall!" Megatron 
gloated as Paddletail entered the frecuency into a small scrabling device. 
Megatron then turned to see the autoguns come to life.
    He took a shot in the leg and fell into cover with Waspinator above him. 
The insect took it out and flew to Megatron. "Are you ok?"
    "Yes! Just get inside that base, I want Kitkat, and I want her bad!" He 
barked as the crossfire dulled with the destruction of another autogun.
    Hell Beast saw Aquarious plummit slighty, and then rise up, taking quick 
blasts at the autoguns. Hell Beast popped over head and saw the hatch. He 
would have to get it open somehow.....
